One of the relays for our front door entrance has malfunctioned and is being replaced. That means that the front entrance will stay locked outside of normal business hours (8am - 5pm) and your fob will not open the door. If you are entering campus after/before standard hours you will need to enter through the back entrance.

Sorry for the inconvenience! We are working to get this fixed as quickly as possible.

<!group> Happy Tax Season! :bookmark_tabs: We've had some students reach out asking about Galvanize and tax reimbursement. Answer: Galvanize is not an accredited institution and uses business loans instead of education loans to cover the cost of tuition. Therefore Galvanize does not distribute tax forms. Lmk if you have any further questions. Best!
